code: public static <T> OptionalConsumer<T> of(Optional<T> optional) {     return new OptionalConsumer<>(optional). }
public OptionalConsumer<T> ifPresent(Consumer<T> c) {     optional.ifPresent(c).     return this. }
public OptionalConsumer<T> ifNotPresent(Runnable r) {     if (!optional.isPresent()) {         r.run().     }     return this. }
